Nicholle Tom https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nicholle_Tom 0 Nicholle Marie Tom (born March 23, 1978) is an American actress. Tom is best known for her roles as Ryce Newton in Beethoven (1992), Beethoven's 2nd (1993), Beethoven (1994–1995), and as Maggie Sheffield on The Nanny. She is also known for voicing Supergirl in the DC Animated Universe. Nicholle_Marie_Tom ( born March_23_,_1978 ) is an_American_actress .
